{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"4294967294","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/contact/layout,_N_T_/contact/page,_N_T_/contact"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"__variable_f367f3\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/3b9d84f248e87f55.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/081a0afca5a9bd20.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-79efdc3d928800db.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-96196b696fe80c1c.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1517-748fb7f6b20d09af.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-2a59eb4b5eb38018.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/8173-3bcd5bf650e85757.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/error-29d01c41823ae36f.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/not-found-6ebff29d556c41cd.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/contact/page-22651f1ce4c71e47.js\" async=\"\"></script><title>Aura | The Intelligent Social Network</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"A modern, premium social network with Dynamic Intelligent Interests.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/icon.svg?03b21b7570e0cb1e\" type=\"image/svg+xml\" sizes=\"any\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"bg-background text-foreground min-h-screen flex flex-col font-sans\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#f7f8fb] text-slate-950\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[1480px] px-6 py-6 sm:px-10 xl:px-12\"><header class=\"flex justify-end rounded-[24px] border border-white/60 bg-white/70 px-5 py-3 backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 transition hover:text-slate-900\" href=\"/?auth=login\">Log in</a><a class=\"rounded-xl bg-[#6f63dd] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#5e53cd]\" href=\"/?auth=signup\">Getting Started</a></div></header><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-2 py-10 sm:px-4 lg:py-14\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary\">Aura</p><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-4xl font-black tracking-[-0.04em] text-[#2e3277] sm:text-5xl\">Contato e caminhos de entrada</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600\">Tudo o que parece interacao aqui leva a um destino real: explorar, entrar, cadastrar ou falar com a equipe.</p></div><div class=\"mt-10\"><section id=\"contact\" class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-18\"><div class=\"grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]\"><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(15,23,42,0.06)] sm:p-8\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary\">Contato</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-[-0.03em] text-slate-950 sm:text-4xl\">Entre na Aura do jeito mais rapido para voce.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-600\">Se voce quer conhecer o produto, entrar na sua conta ou comecar o cadastro agora, a landing ja te leva direto para o proximo passo sem telas mortas.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#6f63dd] px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#5e53cd]\">Criar conta</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-[#d6def6] bg-white px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-[#40458a] transition hover:border-[#bfc9ef]\">Fazer login</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-100\">Ver comunidades</button></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[30px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-950 p-6 text-white shadow-[0_16px_48px_rgba(15,23,42,0.12)] sm:p-8\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-sky-300\">Navegacao publica</p><div class=\"mt-6 space-y-4\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"flex w-full items-center justify-between rounded-2xl bg-white/8 px-4 py-4 text-left transition hover:bg-white/12\"><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Recursos da plataforma</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300\">Veja como feed, reputacao e descoberta funcionam.</p></div><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-sky-300\">Abrir</span></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"flex w-full items-center justify-between rounded-2xl bg-white/8 px-4 py-4 text-left transition hover:bg-white/12\"><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Produto</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300\">Explore a previa publica da experiencia antes de entrar.</p></div><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-sky-300\">Abrir</span></button><a href=\"mailto:contato@aura.social?subject=Contato%20Aura\" class=\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-2xl bg-white/8 px-4 py-4 text-left transition hover:bg-white/12\"><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-white\">Falar com a equipe</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300\">Abra seu cliente de email e envie sua mensagem diretamente.</p></div><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-sky-300\">Email</span></a></div></div></div></section></div></section></div></main><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-79efdc3d928800db.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[87424,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\\\"],\\\"ErrorBoundary\\\"]\\n3:I[32666,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\\\"],\\\"QueryProvider\\\"]\\n4:I[58197,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\\\"],\\\"AuthProvider\\\"]\\n5:I[93351,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\\\"],\\\"SignalingProvider\\\"]\\n6:I[15244,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n7:I[58725,[\\\"8173\\\",\\\"static/chunks/8173-3bcd5bf650e85757.js\\\",\\\"8039\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/error-29d01c41823ae36f.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[43866,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n9:I[65311,[\\\"8173\\\",\\\"static/chunks/8173-3bcd5bf650e85757.js\\\",\\\"